{"tid":626903,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友成日del記錄又講大話","createTime":"2018-04-12T13:27:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T16:51:03.000Z","uid":108978,"like":48,"dislike":858,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"6e4e97fa41c3f78e3e998f6d4001dc208f0afdd1","tid":626903,"uid":108978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T13:27:20.000Z","msg":"之前見到男朋友有同個女仔傾計 我就睇下佢地傾咩啦 <br />\n點知得返一兩句 前面個啲野都del哂<br />\n我問佢做咩要del<br />\n佢就話佢地係無野 係廢事我亂咁諗又發脾氣先會del記錄<br />\n仲話如果我唔信既 可以叫條女cap返啲記錄比我睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見佢講到咁 我咪信佢囉<br />\n個次之後佢應承我唔會再del記錄 點知之後佢又del <br />\n仲要唔只一次 唔明點解應承左唔del都仲要咁做 如果真係無野既 比我睇一睇都唔得？我好少睇佢電話 <br />\n係覺得奇怪先叫佢比我睇<br />\n<br />\n仲有次佢同我講佢同2個朋友出去打邊爐 （個2個朋友係情侶黎）仲拍哂片比我睇 點知原來個次仲有個女仔一齊去 係4人行 但話驚我嬲所以先講大話 話得3個人去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n問佢做咩要講大話又del記錄 <br />\n佢話係因為驚我亂發脾氣亂諗野先會咁<br />\n咁我份人又真係好敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但佢坦白同我講佢同女仔出去<br />\n或者同女仔傾計我唔會唔比<br />\n<br />\n但佢又del哂記錄又講大話 我真係好難唔懷疑<br />\n佢咁樣做呢段關係都無哂信任啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以點做？<br />\n<br />\n係我太敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係條仔有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"142fa28cb808e61c35ce3108e84459a3e8a71a6f","tid":626903,"uid":36435,"like":58,"dislike":1,"score":57,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T13:29:18.000Z","msg":"咁都忍得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7d50d11f6eff1ca4512d9ef942ea210fbefa8aa","tid":626903,"uid":21423,"like":27,"dislike":59,"score":-32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T13:30:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b492434e2948cae8b04f0b03d152cd6d14a0dd7b","tid":626903,"uid":40801,"like":6,"dislike":25,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T13:32:06.000Z","msg":"表面當然佢錯。<br />\n<br />\n愛情基於信任、<br />\n<br />\n沒有信任難以維繫的。"},{"pid":"2be35e01dd0d1efe220dcbb3f23e1de1db3940a2","tid":626903,"uid":153016,"like":87,"dislike":2,"score":85,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T13:33:36.000Z","msg":"可以分手了<br />\n你只會不斷亂諗<br />\n我都經歷過<br />\n最後仲帶埋番屋企搞野"},{"pid":"9d2d9864c3992e51cda11b96e27af4264bd207a8","tid":626903,"uid":84117,"like":86,"dislike":1,"score":85,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T13:35:06.000Z","msg":"醒啦傻妹！！！！<br />\n過來人話你知，有一次就會有第二次。<br />\n你自己諗下，你條仔係冇野，定未有野咋？！<br />\n佢又del record又講大話，你自己知啦，以後嘅路點行落去呀！！！連一段關係之中，最重要嘅「忠誠」都做唔撚到呀！<br />\n你地之間已經出現左信任問題，你一係信，一係唔好信。<br />\n你揀左信嘅，以後唔好再提del record呢件事。"},{"pid":"a3c1a5c82fbee0b622a951988f318e97d9ca3aa4","tid":626903,"uid":67500,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T13:35:06.000Z","msg":"男人唔壞，女人唔愛，預左架啦"},{"pid":"a4af1043b9bb04f71c7afa5b06076f03455c7580","tid":626903,"uid":156122,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T13:45:15.000Z","msg":"Same<br />\n不過係我太敏感佢先乜都唔講<br />\n但其實係佢講嘅野做嘅野都令我冇安全感先咁<br />\n逼緊自己唔好咁care<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cef444d995bed8d6147721f992c0caea912a86c3","tid":626903,"uid":65088,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T14:03:21.000Z","msg":"以為係自己開po<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n男朋友又係同個女仔好fd<br />\n日日傾計叫人做女神<br />\n仲將個對話較做靜音唔俾我見到<br />\n話係唔想我亂諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d171a96ba46bc3f8fddde4a3b5a7b06321feb4b3","tid":626903,"uid":91884,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T14:07:33.000Z","msg":"做咩睇佢電話"},{"pid":"102010c8a93aa241ec7acdcf70e322ecc40da791","tid":626903,"uid":108978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d171a96ba46bc3f8fddde4a3b5a7b06321feb4b3","tid":626903,"uid":91884,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T14:07:33.000Z","msg":"做咩睇佢電話"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T14:09:53.000Z