id":108978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T13:27:20.000Z","msg":"之前見到男朋友有同個女仔傾計 我就睇下佢地傾咩啦 <br />\n點知得返一兩句 前面個啲野都del哂<br />\n我問佢做咩要del<br />\n佢就話佢地係無野 係廢事我亂咁諗又發脾氣先會del記錄<br />\n仲話如果我唔信既 可以叫條女cap返啲記錄比我睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見佢講到咁 我咪信佢囉<br />\n個次之後佢應承我唔會再del記錄 點知之後佢又del <br />\n仲要唔只一次 唔明點解應承左唔del都仲要咁做 如果真係無野既 比我睇一睇都唔得？我好少睇佢電話 <br />\n係覺得奇怪先叫佢比我睇<br />\n<br />\n仲有次佢同我講佢同2個朋友出去打邊爐 （個2個朋友係情侶黎）仲拍哂片比我睇 點知原來個次仲有個女仔一齊去 係4人行 但話驚我嬲所以先講大話 話得3個人去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n問佢做咩要講大話又del記錄 <br />\n佢話係因為驚我亂發脾氣亂諗野先會咁<br />\n咁我份人又真係好敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但佢坦白同我講佢同女仔出去<br />\n或者同女仔傾計我唔會唔比<br />\n<br />\n但佢又del哂記錄又講大話 我真係好難唔懷疑<br />\n佢咁樣做呢段關係都無哂信任啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以點做？<br />\n<br />\n係我太敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係條仔有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T14:44:07.000Z","msg":"其實我信得過佢同啲女仔係普通朋友既關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我想佢可以對我坦白 唔好成日講大話同del記錄  如果佢話驚我又亂諗野 咁對我坦白唔del記錄真係最好既方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好屌我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"280d415a8e4e67c1302f367e63ce4f1710762928","tid":626903,"uid":61271,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T14:48:03.000Z","msg":"要幾天真先仲會信無啦啦會del 對話紀錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04b714eb48d7687147b67422de6c5defbc3d1e68","tid":626903,"uid":165510,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T14:49:46.000Z","msg":"講咩垃圾廢話咩驚你嬲驚你發脾氣先del真係最on9<br />\n你咁諗得都知成件事有問題啦<br />\n咁樣仲做證明佢都有問題 <br />\n唔好信咩無下次 假㗎 睇你下次發唔發現到姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec461f907237db7fadcd680f64dc2539c36d99bd","tid":626903,"uid":108978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"280d415a8e4e67c1302f367e63ce4f1710762928","tid":626903,"uid":61271,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T14:48:03.000Z","msg":"要幾天真先仲會信無啦啦會del 對話紀錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T14:53:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真心咩"},{"pid":"2e9caa6fb216f0c4a37e9914ae39652881adb90c","tid":626903,"uid":14131,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T14:54:32.000Z","msg":"投嘜鳩野票呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n投完過萬票就講分手咩<br />\n睇死你係度哭訴完<br />\n轉頭又返去幫你男朋友含撚含到雪雪聲啦<br />\n女人又要呻又要唔捨得分手<br />\n我見得多啦！已經至少安慰過兩位數臭閪<br />\n隔一排見住佢地比人飛都重要挽留真係好撚爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe169082f63431c84ea24bd294da6b173b04d9c7","tid":626903,"uid":76680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T14:59:01.000Z","msg":"樓主點知你男朋友del左紀錄？"},{"pid":"6d46d4b195cbe238b88ee1f01a1df7d4526112c9","tid":626903,"uid":71176,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:00:36.000Z","msg":"放心一定係同條女有嘢先會del<br />\n我男朋友都係咁 我會左佢 最後出咗軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4ed877bb4ef4dd16676a12f7a21fa2840fa4ede","tid":626903,"uid":71176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:01:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>放心一定係同條女有嘢先會del<br />\n我男朋友都係咁 我信左佢 最後出咗軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"c2e938494c927a778fc